<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>Complete your Solar Maket signup</title>
  <style>
    body{margin:0;padding:0;background:#06080d;font-family:'DM Sans',Arial,sans-serif;color:#e2e8f0}
    .wrap{max-width:560px;margin:40px auto;background:#111827;border:1px solid #1e293b;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden}
    .header{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#111827,#162032);padding:32px;text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid #1e293b}
    .logo{font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#f59e0b;letter-spacing:1px}
    .body{padding:36px}
    h2{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#e2e8f0;margin:0 0 12px}
    p{color:#94a3b8;font-size:15px;line-height:1.65;margin:0 0 16px}
    .otp-box{background:#162032;border:2px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.3);border-radius:10px;padding:24px;text-align:center;margin:24px 0}
    .otp{font-size:40px;font-weight:700;color:#f59e0b;letter-spacing:12px;font-family:monospace}
    .otp-note{font-size:13px;color:#475569;margin-top:8px}
    .highlight{background:rgba(245,158,11,0.08);border-left:3px solid #f59e0b;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;padding:12px 16px;margin:16px 0}
    .footer{padding:20px 36px;border-top:1px solid #1e293b;text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:#475569}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="header"><div class="logo">☀️ Solar Maket</div></div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>You're almost in, {{firstName}}!</h2>
      <p>You created a Solar Maket account but haven't verified your email yet. Use the code below to complete your signup and start buying or selling solar equipment.</p>
      <div class="otp-box">
        <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>
        <div class="otp-note">Expires in 10 minutes. Do not share with anyone.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="highlight">
        <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px">Once verified you can browse thousands of solar products, hire certified engineers and get a personalised system recommendation.</p>
      </div>
      <p>If you didn't create this account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">© {{year}} Solar Maket Nigeria. All rights reserved.</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
